        h1 Celebrating Love at the Gardens of the World
        p Who doesnâ€™t like a love story? This is a story about Adela and Cristi on a recent trip to Berlin when the cherry trees where just flowering. Every time we are around them they show a lot of emotion and candid feelings. Therefore we wanted to give them a present, a photo session to capture those real moments, the ones that kids or grandkids could look back on later and say, wow, they REALLY love each other! 

